To see network interface : 
    ip link
    ifconfig  -a
    for ubuntu cat /etv/network/interfaces
   
 To see ipadress
    ifconfig ens3 <Network interface>
To learn mac address
    ip link 
    
 ssh node01 ifconfig ens3
 
 To learn which route :
 ip r 
 
 what is the port listening :
 netstat -natulp | grep * | grep LISTEN
   
